The Management of Kano Electricity Distribution Company (KEDCO) on Thursday felicitated with all Christian faithful and the general public as the world marks this year’s Christmas and Boxing Day celebrations. According to the Management, the season presents an opportunity for everyone to show love and care especially for those who are in need in view of the essence of Christmas. Dr Jamil Isyaku Gwamna, the Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer KEDCO, said “ we owe humanity the care that they deserved and every moment like this present opportunities to touch lives in that regard.” EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! “ I wish all the Christian community within Kano franchise and beyond a wonderful celebration and in line with the purpose of the season, we must love and tolerate one another for the good of the society and the unity of Nigeria.” Dr Gwamna, however, cautioned Nigerians not to take for granted the need to stay safe while celebrating, adding that their health must be prioritised during the festivities as their own contribution to the fight against COVID-19. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION